üß© Task 1 ‚Äî Initial Character Assessment

Goal
Obtain for each character ‚Äî Deadpool, Wolverine, the Hound of the Baskervilles, Sherlock Holmes, Dr. Watson ‚Äî a short description and Top-3 important facts. Define the output format (text length, formatting).

Actions performed

Create a prompt in ChatGPT/Gemini requesting:

a concise bio and Top-3 facts for each listed character;

a clear, uniform formatting template (e.g., bullet lists, ‚â§3‚Äì4 sentences per bio);

explicit instruction to stay within task scope (no extra sources yet).

Save prompt and output screenshots.

Screenshots
none

