üß© Task 2 ‚Äî Main vs. Supporting Roles (with Role Prompting)

Goal
Ask ChatGPT for advice on which characters should be main and which should be supporting, based on Task 1 results. Assign a role to ChatGPT (e.g., ‚ÄúYou are a professional film script editor‚Ä¶‚Äù).

Actions performed

Prepare a prompt that:

summarizes Task 1 outputs;

assigns ChatGPT a professional role;

requests a clear split into Main vs Supporting roles;

enforces consistent formatting (two lists).

Save prompt and output screenshots.

