üß© Task 3 ‚Äî Who Appeared First: Deadpool or Wolverine (Wikipedia-only)

Goal
Determine who appeared earlier in pop culture ‚Äî Deadpool or Wolverine ‚Äî using only:

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deadpool

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wolverine_(character)

Define the search sequence (which character to check first) and the output format (e.g., ‚Äúbirth/first appearance info for Deadpool‚Äù, ‚Äúbirth/first appearance info for Wolverine‚Äù). End with a clear statement who is older.

Actions performed

Write a prompt that:

limits the model to the two Wikipedia pages;

specifies the order of lookup;

specifies exact output fields;

requires a final comparative verdict (‚Äúwho is older‚Äù).

Save screenshots of the prompt and the result.

Screenshots
none

