üß© Task 8 ‚Äî Prompt to Generate the First Script Chapter

Goal
Create a single prompt to generate the first chapter of the movie script. The text must include Deadpool, Wolverine, the Hound of the Baskervilles, Sherlock Holmes, Dr. Watson, plus two supporting characters (selected from Task 6‚Äì7). The script must contain dialogues that incorporate answers from Tasks 4‚Äì5 (facts about Deadpool and Wolverine) and must include a joke about who is older (from Task 3). You must assign a role to ChatGPT for generation.

Actions performed

Build a role-prompt (e.g., ‚ÄúYou are a professional screenwriter‚Ä¶‚Äù).

Include explicit constraints: characters, dialogues using prior Q&A, the ‚Äúwho is older‚Äù joke, continuity with Tasks 6‚Äì7 for supporting roles.

Save prompt and output screenshots.

